title: Bobby's Cowboy Photoshoot With Ronnie Dunn Of Brooks and Dunn + Lunchbox Demands Money From Our Boss + Darius Rucker Asked If People Still Call Him ‘Hootie’
itunes:title: Bobby's Cowboy Photoshoot With Ronnie Dunn Of Brooks and Dunn + Lunchbox Demands Money From Our Boss + Darius Rucker Asked If People Still Call Him ‘Hootie’
description:
Bobby talks about his cowboy photoshoot with Ronnie Dunn from Brooks and Dunn. Lunchbox showed up to a station event, but no one had told him it was cancelled. He decided to go see the boss with a hidden mic and demand payment. Plus, Chris Janson and Darius Rucker call in to talk about their new music out today!
